  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Recap & News 10-5-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping recent Star Atlas news.\nMetaverse Nomads #167 Star Atlas w/ King Bryan, DRUMCARL05 and TH James\nMetaverse Nomads posted their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nStar Atlas Founders Panel – Impact Summit 2024\nStar Atlas posted a video of their founders talking at their conference.\nSTAR ATLAS #254 Daily Atlas Emissions, Most Stable In History!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of Star Atlas updates.\nWeekly Star Atlas Newsletter #150\nAephia posted their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas – Preseason Development Sneak Peek\nStar Atlas posted a video of ongoing game development.\nThe Atlas Brew #131\nStar Atlas TV posted video of the latest Atlas Brew.\nWhat Sets Star Atlas Apart: Impact Summit Economy\nOCG Thor posted a video talking about the Star Atlas economy.\nStar Atlas Brew #131: DAO Council Debate – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recapping the latest Atlas Brew.",
